		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="154">Osvaldo Myconio</persName>, antistiti ecclesiae <placeName ref="97">Basileiensis</placeName>, domino et fratri venerando et dilecto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et vitae innocentiam a domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non admodum valemus fratres tui, carissime <persName ref="154">Myconi</persName>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="114">Leo</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="114">Leo Jud</persName>.</note> propemodum agit animam.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="14">Bibliander</persName>, vir incomparabilis, morbo articulari an podagrae laboret, incertum; sind gschwüstergete kind<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">sind gschwüstergete kind <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Geschwisterkinder (im Sinne von: ähnlich geartet).</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Graviter certe laborat, interea aeger obambulat ac pro more praelegit.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam totus ab omnibus abstineret lectionibus, quod is tam constanter recusat, quam<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>In der Vorlage wohl irrtümlich</hi> quum.</note> pertinaciter nos exigimus.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="145">Megander</persName> et ipse aegrotat et concionatur tamen.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Me vero inclementiss[ima] febris iam dies aliquot vexavit.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">14. hodie dies agitur, quo ultimum aedes egressus sum.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deliteo domi et cum tertiana<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Wechselfieber mit dreitägigem Zyklus (Malaria tertiana); vgl. Max <hi>Höfler,</hi> Deutsches Krankheitsnamen-Buch, München 1899 (Nachdruck: Hildesheim-New York 1970), S. 144. 734.</note> aeger conflictor.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sentio tamen vim morbi nonnihil remittere.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus adsit nobis et restituat nos, si placemus ipsi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caseum hunc, quaeso, fide summa <persName ref="1176">Richardo</persName> Hiltzio<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="1176">Richard Hilles</persName>.</note> Anglo Argentinam perferri curato.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rem feceris gratissimam.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praetium ipse persolvam, ubi indicaris.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec boni consule; nam plura non potui.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale cum omnibus tuis.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te fratres omnes.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">19. aprilis 1542.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus H. Bullingerus.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
